node.text:
During my isolation it was tough not being able to gym, but had to find the motivation to get some type of sweat in so I came up with a few workouts, so here’s a good one! try this if you’re stuck in the house or if your gym isn’t open!

-30 sec jump rope
-30 sec in and out squat jumps
-30 sec RDL to squat
-30 sec lunge up jumps
-30 sec alt side plank twists

Wearing my own @get_tighterr sweat belt to make me feel tight and to sweat a little extra durning my HIIT workouts 😁 you can pre order yours with the link in my bio! 
Sizes S-XXL (true to size)
I’m wearing a medium

node.text:
You guys I’m OBSESSED with this dessert..
Literally every night I make this and eat it after dinner.
Here’s my little tutorial on how I make it!
- 3 egg whites
- 1 scoop @iammotiv8 dessert protein
- 2 TBS coca powder
- 1/2 cup plain pumpkin.
- dash baking powder 
Mix all together and bake on parchment paper for 15-20 min on 350 degrees.
Brownie by it’s self is around d 200 cal and it’s a pretty big size!

If you try this recipe let me know!!
————-
If you want to try this protein use my code MOTIV8JESSICA for free shipping!
This is cookie dough protein, their blueberry is also amazingggg.

node.text:
It’s ALL a mindset.

Success comes to those who put forth the consistent and persistent effort and YOU are the only one who can make that happen.

You could see a thousand transformation pictures and a million motivational quotes, but your mind is going to be the tool that gets you where you want to be. 

Fill it with positivity, you got this ✨
—————-
Click the link in my bio for my 4 week at home program! 

This program is designed for anyone looking for guidance on getting a good workout in without a gym.

If you have dumbbells and resistance bands you’re all set! 💪🏽

-4 weeks consisting of 
•abs everyday
•HIIT warm up
•2 upper body days
•2 lower body days
•1 full body day
•recovery stretches 

Each exercise in the program is performed so you understand how to do it. 

Getfitwjessica.com or link in bio 🤗

node.text:
Put on a cute gym outfit that makes you feel confident and WORK ITTTT!!

Today was leg dayyyy, super set every 2 workouts. 12x4 of every superset.

I record my workouts to give ideas. I know it’s not easy walking into a gym and feeling clueless on what to do, so steal whatever you want 😉 

Outfit from @karollbrazilsportswear 💕 check her website! Affordable workout clothes that are flipping SO CUTE and sassy 😜

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Jessica on July 20, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, activewear and outdoors.

node.text:
Never in a million years would 2016 Jessica ever think she’d be here today repping a workout clothing brand, in a sports bra and printed leggings… it’s the non scale victories I over came that are so rewarding that came along with this journey. 

Feeling so proud and and thankful. Everyday is a new beginning and I hope you all remember that🙏🏽💕 

Sports bra and leggings from @buffbunny_collection 
- Getfitwjessica = support 🤗

📸 @babiczvideo

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Jessica on July 19, 2021 tagging @naturesownbread, and @thelaughingcowusa. May be an image of food.

node.text:
I don’t care, I could eat this, everyday. Single. Day. And I won’t get sick of it 🤤 

Seared up some salmon and put it on some avocado toast!
I also spread @thelaughingcowusa cheese in the toast before the avocado and it makes all the difference, I’m OBSESSED !!! 

Sprinkle on pink salt and Italian seasoning and thank me later sushi lovers! 😉
